<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Block Rezidential | Debt Recovery Services</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #000000;
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560448204-e02f11c3d0e2?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #cccccc;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #cccccc;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .service-item {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .service-item img {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
        }

        .service-item h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .service-item p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        .about-image {
            display: block;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
        }

        .contact-info {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #000000;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #cccccc;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            section h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            nav ul {
                gap: 15px;
            }

            nav ul li a {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .service-item img {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="#" class="logo">Block Rezidential</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Protect Your Home with Block Rezidential</h1>
            <p>Expert debt recovery services to help you keep your home and achieve financial stability.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
        <h2>Our Solutions</h2>
        <p>We offer a range of services to help you navigate financial challenges and protect your home.</p>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-item">
                <img src="images/debt-restructuring.jpg" alt="Debt Restructuring">
                <h3>Debt Restructuring</h3>
                <p>Negotiate with lenders to create affordable repayment plans tailored to your needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Foreclosure Prevention">
                <h3>Foreclosure Prevention</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive strategies to stop foreclosure and keep you in your home.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Loss Mitigation">
                <h3>Loss Mitigation</h3>
                <p>Explore all options to reduce financial strain and avoid default.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560523159-4a9692d222ef?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=80&q=80" alt="Short Sale Assistance">
                <h3>Short Sale Assistance</h3>
                <p>Expert guidance for selling your home to settle debts responsibly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>At Block Rezidential, we are dedicated to helping homeowners overcome financial challenges and keep their homes. With years of experience and a team of trusted professionals, we negotiate with lenders to find the best solutions for our clients. Your peace of mind is our priority.</p>
        <img src="images/about-team.jpg" alt="Our Team" class="about-image">
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Ready to protect your home? Reach out for a consultation today.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>9440 Santa Monica Boulevard, Suite 301<br>Beverly Hills, California 90210<br>United States</p>
            <p>Email: info@blockrezidential.com<br>Phone: (310) 555-1234</p>
            <a href="mailto:info@blockrezidential.com" class="cta-button">Schedule a Consultation</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2025 Block Rezidential. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Smooth scrolling for navigation links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
                    behavior: 'smooth'
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>